<h1>Welcome to NexGen</h1>

<p>Since January 1, 2003 NexGen Productions. Ltd. has provided C2C production services... from "Conception to Completion" and on March 6, 2007 NexGen started offering real-time uncompressed HD video production services.</p>

<p>NexGen's equipment and expertise give us the edge over our competition by providing cost effective efficiency. Real-time non-proxy HD editing practically eliminates waiting on extended renders which can cost you time and money, not to mention the wear and tear on your patience.</p>

<p>NexGen's services include editing, field production, 3D and 2D animation, graphic design, compositing, Blu-ray and DVD authoring, 5.1 Surround Sound editing and encoding, digital media transcoding and encoding for web and mobile devices, and real-time video up converting and down converting between SD and HD footage.
</p>

<p>We build projects for HD broadcasts worldwide; we produce commercials for local, regional, and national broadcasts; and we convert projects to digital media for distribution to theaters around the world in 2K.</p>

<p>Need a banner ad for a web page or an animated logo? Maybe you need an animation that visually demonstrates your concept as a virtual working prototype.  NexGen's C2C production services can fulfill your needs. From Concept to completion, NexGen has the crew, the expertise, and the <a href="toolsPg/toolsHome.html">Tools</a> to complete your video project. NexGen is truly "Changing the Way You Communicate".</p>

<p>Please take a few minutes and browse the rest of our  site. If you have a potential project you would like to discuss further, and for  more examples of our work, visit the <span class="smCap"><a href="aboutUs/aboutUs.html">About Us</a></span> page and please <a href="contactPg/contactUs.html">Contact Us</a>.</p>

<p>Some areas of our site maybe under construction so please re-visit us soon.</p>


